  <p><prosody rate="86%">Listen and repeat.</prosody></p>
  <p><prosody rate="86%">classroom.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">classroom.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">can/can't.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">can/can't.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">grammar.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">grammar.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">Places,.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/><p><prosody rate="86%">Places,.</prosody></p><break time="700ms"/>
  <p><prosody rate="86%">Now say the full sentence.</prosody></p>
  <p><prosody rate="86%">Example 1: I can use can/can't to talk about classroom.</prosody></p>
